# API (@asto/api)

- Entry: `src/index.ts` → `src/app.ts` → `src/routes.ts`
- **AI routes** (`src/routes/ai-routes.ts`): mobil `lib/ai-api.ts` — günlük öngörü, chart narrative, ask, sinastri
- **Legacy routes** (`src/routes/legacy-routes.ts`): auth, `/me`, partner CRUD, tokens — yalnızca JSON store / eski istemciler
- Auth: Firebase ID token; `requireAuth` + `store.userFromToken` (Admin SDK verify)
- Harita: `packages/shared/src/chart/engine.ts` — mobil ve API aynı engine
- AI: `src/ai.ts` — `GEMINI_API_KEY` veya `OPENAI_API_KEY`; yoksa mock
- Persist: `store-firestore.ts` (production) veya `store.ts` → `data/db.json` (local)
- Jeton: `store.adjustTokens`; maliyetler `@asto/shared` TOKEN_COSTS
- Hata: `{ error: string }` JSON
- Yeni **AI** endpoint: `ai-routes.ts` + `apps/mobile/lib/ai-api.ts` + `ai-service.ts` + `docs/API.md`
